Name: Rifle Strike
About the game: A new fast-paced FPS shooter FOR FREE! Enjoy a First Person shooter the way I wanted to see it! The full release will contain: - Various maps and gamemodes - Unique weapons, weapon camos - Scorestreaks - Single-Player - Co-op - Progression system This game is and will be completely micro-transaction free! You will never have to pay to get better equipment! Weapons are accessible through cash earned during a match. This whole game is being developed by me, a single person, so please understand that! My goal is simply to make a fun free to play game.
